pr_title: Provide JSON serilization feature and KBox python distribution
pr_body:
# Purpose
This PR will provide two main features.
* JSON serialization for KBox, which will convert the KBox output into JSON String.
* KBox python distribution

This will also resolve the following issues in KBox
* resolve #26 
* resolve #23

pr_title: Add instruction about KBox python package in README.md
Provide latest KBox functionalities to airML
pr_body:
# Purpose
This PR will provide the latest KBox features to airML. Now airML can be used to manage and distribute ML models at scale. Read the updated [README.md](https://github.com/sahandilshan/airML-1/blob/master/README.md) file for more information.

## Features
* Serialize KBox command output into JSON format
* Directly execute commands via terminal
* provide the following methods to execute KBox commands in a python environment
     * execute(commands)
     * list(kns=False)
     * install(modelID, format=None, version=None)
     * getInfo(model)
     * locate(modelID, format, version=None)
     * search(pattern, format, version=None)
